title: Terry and Jo's Food for Thought
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Burritos, nachos, and some sandwiches are lacto-vegetarian suitable and could be made vegan by requesting no cheese, etc. Pizzas could be made vegan, and there is a veggie heaven pizza. Most smoothies are vegan, some salads are vegan, others request for no cheese.
